{"tid":2268429,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–以中性pH7的方式染髮","createTime":"2020-11-02T22:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T13:36:49.000Z","uid":38861,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"94c6c9df8336013c778470c4ef25f018e46e8b07","tid":2268429,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:31:11.000Z","msg":"黑色的秀髮，最主要是由真黑素(Eumelanin)天然染成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JnybOR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJnybOR4.jpg&h=b1ecb39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）皮膚下的黑素細胞(Melanocyte)會製造出黑色粒子Melanosomes，而這些黑色粒子Melanosomes會走到表皮(Epidermis)或者髮囊(Hair follicile)，賦予皮膚及頭髮黑色外表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNL9Axb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNL9Axb.png&h=1bcf2e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）圖中為Melanosomes裡頭的生物化學反應，起始材料為氨基酸，經過一輪酶素的化學反應後，最終成品將為黑色真黑素及啡色真黑素。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeXjXLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeXjXLy.png&h=325eb88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而根據兩者比例的不同，最終的顏色效果亦會有所不同，所以Melanosomes並不一定是純黑色，亦因而解釋了為何並不是所有人的頭髮也是漆黑黑一片。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，這一系列發生在Melanosomes的反應均是在中性pH7的環境下進行，有別於現時常用的鹼性pH化學染髮方式。<br />\n<br />\n有科學家看準這一點，因而嘗試照辦煮碗在體外套用我們自身Melanosomes蛋白酶的機制方式進行染髮（Ref1)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）從圖中可見，鹼性pH化學染髮以及中性pH7模仿人類Melanosomes裡頭生物化學反應方式染髮（2小時，攝氏35度），兩者最終的外表差別不大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjkUMD1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjkUMD1.png&h=57ff1ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且經過5次清水沖洗及10分鐘的洗髮水猛烈沖洗後，兩者亦沒有出現脫色的現象。<br />\n<br />\n只不過，利用鹼性pH化學染髮的話，色素會徹底進入髮質內部。<br />\n反觀中性pH7生物化學反應方式染髮，色素主要聚集在髮質外部，因此對頭髮的傷害相對較低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）在圖中亦可以清楚看得到，鹼性pH化學染髮對頭髮外部會做成傷害(箭嘴所指位置)，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fG3y2cv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfG3y2cv.png&h=19cd105b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而中性pH7模仿人類Melanosomes裡頭生物化學反應方式染髮則沒有這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n此方法能否在日後淘汰鹼性pH化學染髮或其他的染髮手段，我們將可拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EsQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=a39c5fb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EsQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=e7981ece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EsQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=05d350e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubs.acs.org/doi/pdf/10.1021/acs.chemmater.0c02790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubs.acs.org%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1021%2Facs.chemmater.0c02790&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EsQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=8b19111e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubs.acs.org/doi/pdf/10.1021/acs.chemmater.0c02790</a>"},{"pid":"da169b269ea33abbb3c91b6d818afcebb1cc834f","tid":2268429,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f31d346603c1ab77cae120b8763f9ea621afe5e3","tid":2268429,"uid":326043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:35:52.000Z","msg":"我用檸檬汁染<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搽咗上頭曬10分鐘太陽<br />\n利申：唔知傷唔傷 試吓自己會唔會敏感"},{"pid":"471091018425b2b98550a45a4d2483e7c0ab9498","tid":2268429,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f31d346603c1ab77cae120b8763f9ea621afe5e3","tid":2268429,"uid":326043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:35:52.000Z","msg":"我用檸檬汁染<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搽咗上頭曬10分鐘太陽<br />\n利申：唔知傷唔傷 試吓自己會唔會敏感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />檸檬汁染？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42010aa8e71adfd60945d212a96bbc717b0f544","tid":2268429,"uid":326043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"471091018425b2b98550a45a4d2483e7c0ab9498","tid":2268429,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f31d346603c1ab77cae120b8763f9ea621afe5e3","tid":2268429,"uid":326043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:35:52.000Z","msg":"我用檸檬汁染<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搽咗上頭曬10分鐘太陽<br />\n利申：唔知傷唔傷 試吓自己會唔會敏感"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />檸檬汁染？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T22:37:14.000Z","msg":"Yea 幾work 啡啡地"},{"pid":"83b32555d676